<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Musician"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Porter Robinson"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Sarah Midori Perry"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Gus Lobban"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Nurture"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="1839140774"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="1824597603"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="USQE92000196"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="235518886"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="chan-air"/></metadata></head><body dur="03:42.847"><div begin="00:18.456" end="03:42.847"><p begin="00:18.456" end="00:23.017" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L0">No, I don't miss the feeling anymore<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不，我不再怀念那种感觉</span></p><p begin="00:23.017" end="00:26.685" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1">Yeah, I want something new to love<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是的，我渴望新的爱</span></p><p begin="00:26.685" end="00:28.656" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2">I was so nostalgic<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我曾如此怀旧</span></p><p begin="00:28.656" end="00:30.739" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3">But I'm fine without it<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但没有它，我亦安然</span></p><p begin="00:30.739" end="00:34.463" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4">You don't really want what you think you want<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你所求的，非你真欲</span></p><p begin="00:34.463" end="00:36.955" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5">No, I don't wanna lose it<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不，我不想失去它</span></p><p begin="00:36.955" end="00:38.676" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6">This emotion<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这份情感</span></p><p begin="00:38.676" end="00:42.383" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7">Yeah, I just wanna do everything<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是的，我愿倾尽所有</span></p><p begin="00:42.383" end="00:44.333" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8">I get so excited<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当我心潮澎湃</span></p><p begin="00:44.333" end="00:46.536" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9">When I finally find it<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">当我终于寻得</span></p><p begin="00:46.536" end="00:50.473" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10">It just gets brighter from now on<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">从此世界愈发绚烂</span></p><p begin="00:50.939" end="00:54.503" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11">Then you sigh:<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你轻叹道：</span></p><p begin="00:54.503" end="00:59.393" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12">"You know I love you, so I think I should tell you, Porter<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">"你知我深爱于你，故我当告你，Porter</span></p><p begin="00:59.393" end="01:06.520" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13">This life: isn't it time that you grow up?"<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这艺术之路，该是时候成长了？"</span></p><p begin="01:07.008" end="01:09.438" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14">Oh, it's calling<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">哦，它在召唤</span></p><p begin="01:09.438" end="01:13.459" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15">I just can't stop, I'm sorry<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我无法停下，纵然愧疚</span></p><p begin="01:13.459" end="01:16.440" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16">I can feel a new day dawning<span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:18.783" end="01:21.623">(I shouldn't do this to myself)<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不该如此自毁</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我已感知黎明微光</span></p><p begin="01:18.783" end="01:21.623" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17">I shouldn't do this to myself<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不该如此自毁</span></p><p begin="01:22.975" end="01:25.731" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18">But sincerely<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">然而，我诚心相告</span></p><p begin="01:25.731" end="01:29.474" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19">Can't you feel what I'm feeling?<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你仍无法感知我内心吗？</span></p><p begin="01:29.474" end="01:32.208" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20">I can see my life so clearly<span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:34.767" end="01:38.516">(I shouldn't do this to myself)<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不该如此自毁</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我的生命此刻澄澈</span></p><p begin="01:34.767" end="01:38.516" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21">I shouldn't do this to myself<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不该如此自毁</span></p><p begin="01:38.701" end="01:41.032" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22">Well, this is why we do it<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这便是我们为何执着</span></p><p begin="01:41.032" end="01:43.184" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23">For the feeling<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">为那纯粹的悸动</span></p><p begin="01:43.184" end="01:44.991" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L24">How do you do music?<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">音乐之道何在？</span></p><p begin="01:44.991" end="01:46.833" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L25">Well, it's easy:<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">其实简单：</span></p><p begin="01:46.833" end="01:48.650" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L26">You just face your fears and<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你只需直面恐惧</span></p><p begin="01:48.650" end="01:50.719" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L27">You become your heroes<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">便成为自己的英雄</span></p><p begin="01:50.719" end="01:54.328" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L28">I don't understand why you're freaking out<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不懂你为何如此惊惶</span></p><p begin="01:54.617" end="01:55.760" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L29">Then they say:<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">他们道：</span></p><p begin="01:55.760" end="02:00.596" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L30">"Fine, well do what you need to<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">"好吧，做你认定之事</span></p><p begin="02:00.596" end="02:02.655" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L31">But I don't want to see you<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但我不愿见你</span></p><p begin="02:02.655" end="02:06.554" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L32">Wasting your life<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">虚掷光阴</span></p><p begin="02:06.554" end="02:10.722" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L33">Isn't it time you get a job?"<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">该是时候安定下来了吧？"</span></p><p begin="02:10.907" end="02:13.428" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L34">Oh, it's calling<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">哦，它在召唤</span></p><p begin="02:13.428" end="02:17.675" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L35">I just can't stop, I'm sorry<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我无法停下，纵然愧疚</span></p><p begin="02:17.675" end="02:20.238" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L36">I can feel a new day dawning<span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="02:22.930" end="02:26.314">(I shouldn't do this to myself)<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不该如此自毁</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我已感知黎明微光</span></p><p begin="02:22.930" end="02:26.314" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L37">I shouldn't do this to myself<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不该如此自毁</span></p><p begin="02:26.927" end="02:29.414" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L38">But sincerely<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">然而，我诚心相告</span></p><p begin="02:29.414" end="02:33.594" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L39">Can't you feel what I'm feeling?<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你仍无法感知我内心吗？</span></p><p begin="02:33.594" end="02:36.478" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L40">I can see my life so clearly<span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="02:38.838" end="02:42.877">(I shouldn't do this to myself)<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不该如此自毁</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我的生命此刻澄澈</span></p><p begin="02:38.838" end="02:42.877" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L41">I shouldn't do this to myself<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不该如此自毁</span></p><p begin="02:59.085" end="03:01.541" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L42">But sincerely<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">然而，我诚心相告</span></p><p begin="03:01.541" end="03:05.574" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L43">Can't you feel what I'm feeling?<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你仍无法感知我内心吗？</span></p><p begin="03:05.574" end="03:09.176" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L44">I can see my life so clearly<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我的生命此刻澄澈</span></p><p begin="03:09.176" end="03:11.470" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L45">And I know it doesn't last<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我知这光芒终将消逝</span></p><p begin="03:11.470" end="03:14.869" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L46">But I don't mind at all anymore<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">但此刻，我已不再忧惧</span></p><p begin="03:14.994" end="03:17.474" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L47">Oh, it's calling<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">哦，它在召唤</span></p><p begin="03:17.474" end="03:21.587" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L48">I just can't stop, I'm sorry<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我无法停下，纵然愧疚</span></p><p begin="03:21.587" end="03:24.681" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L49">I can feel a new day dawning<span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="03:27.020" end="03:30.458">(I shouldn't do this to myself)<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不该如此自毁</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我已感知黎明微光</span></p><p begin="03:27.020" end="03:30.458" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L50">I shouldn't do this to myself<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不该如此自毁</span></p><p begin="03:31.131" end="03:33.417" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L51">But sincerely<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">然而，我诚心相告</span></p><p begin="03:33.417" end="03:37.583" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L52">Can't you feel what I'm feeling?<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你仍无法感知我内心吗？</span></p><p begin="03:37.583" end="03:40.398" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L53">I can see my life so clearly (翻译：我眼见着自己的人生明朗开来)<span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="03:42.847" end="03:42.847">(I shouldn't do this to myself)<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不该如此自毁</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你仍无法感知我内心吗？</span></p><p begin="03:42.847" end="03:42.847" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L54">I shouldn't do this to myself<span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不该如此自毁</span></p></div></body></tt>